---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of use — Pholio"
  description="Terms of use for Pholio — plain language rules for using the website and mobile app."
  lang="en"
  schemaType="WebSite"
>
  <section class="max-page ptitle">
    <nav class="crumb"><a href="/">PHOLIO</a><span class="sep">→</span><span class="cur">TERMS</span></nav>
    <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-top:24px">Effective 01 Jan 2026</div>
    <h1 class="hero-h1" style="margin-top:16px">Terms of use.</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="max-page" style="padding-bottom:96px">
    <div class="max-prose prose-ed">
      <p class="drop-cap">By using this website or the Pholio app, you agree to these terms. We've tried to write them in plain language. If anything is unclear, email us at <a href="mailto:legal@pholio.co">legal@pholio.co</a> and we'll explain.</p>

      <h2>1. Content</h2>
      <p>Articles on this site are published by Pholio Media Ltd. You may quote up to 150 words with attribution and a link. Republishing entire articles without permission is not allowed.</p>

      <h2>2. Accuracy</h2>
      <p>We make a reasonable effort to keep every answer current, but prices, hours, and local conditions change. Always confirm time-sensitive details directly before travelling.</p>

      <h2>3. User submissions</h2>
      <p>If you submit a question, correction, or tip, you grant us a perpetual, non-exclusive license to publish it in edited form on this site and in the app, with or without attribution as you prefer.</p>

      <h2>4. Subscriptions</h2>
      <p>App subscriptions renew automatically until cancelled. You can cancel at any time through your Apple or Google account. We don't issue pro-rata refunds for the remainder of a billing period.</p>

      <h2>5. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>Pholio is a publication, not a travel agent. We're not responsible for any loss or inconvenience arising from travel decisions you make after reading our content.</p>

      <h2>6. Governing law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Vietnam. Any dispute will be resolved by the courts of Hanoi.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
